09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開始擔心畢業要出嚟乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊個唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyear1嗰陣覺得畢業仲係好遠嘅事所以冇擔心過<br />\n近排先開始發現時間過得太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最慘既係，傳說中最自由既地方，原來都只係追求現實既場所，理想既代價從來無少過</blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直以為自己好努力就可以追尋到自己嘅理想<br />\n但係嗰咁現實嘅地方 理想根本就係垃圾 冇人在乎 <br />\n到最後 自己都可能為咗生存而放棄理想 盲目去迎合呢個現實嘅世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咩理想 可唔可以講下？</blockquote><br />\n都唔知算唔算理想 可能會畀人覺得幼稚"},{"pid":"0c3cc72d624e9000c12bac3e1ac9f2204b7dc70d","tid":125694,"uid":656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>讀緊非八大，但係自己中意嘅野<br />\n但係爛爛爛爛gpa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專門行業？</blockquote><br />\n唔係呀<br />\n讀緊中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1c533c17da4be8be1b454e56de4a598eef0cd9","tid":125694,"uid":30335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:21:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開始擔心畢業要出嚟乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊個唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyear1嗰陣覺得畢業仲係好遠嘅事所以冇擔心過<br />\n近排先開始發現時間過得太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打讀咩科</blockquote><br />\nsocial嘥銀時<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n次次俾人問畢業出嚟可以做咩都口啞啞<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係ba仔 都係三大乞食科之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa8d23e4a7ef4cbeff476862ebc2730c2ddcb89","tid":125694,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:22:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開始擔心畢業要出嚟乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊個唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyear1嗰陣覺得畢業仲係好遠嘅事所以冇擔心過<br />\n近排先開始發現時間過得太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n永遠都有好多事阻礙個 想 字<br />\n<br />\n就好似係大學，reg乜都要睇住個grade，想reg既一係就成抽pre requisite，一係就無credit，一係無位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連想自由揀course 都唔得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家成日加d 九唔搭八既project，唔係怕同人溝通，而係咁多科加埋，其實都好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n中學成日比老師呃鳩我入大學好自由又開心又唔洗讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係佢地年代，無幾多人會全力追hon，呢樣個樣，個陣入到中，港大已經係人中之龍，經濟又係最急速發展，的確輕鬆d。<br />\n<br />\n只可以話佢地都離開左個圈子好耐。"},{"pid":"a287b733a45793a5336b08f5579ec4a55322b807","tid":125694,"uid":2141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:23:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n都唔知算唔算理想 可能會畀人覺得幼稚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔想再做機器 好想改變呢個社會 唔想學生只係死讀書 想佢哋知自己究竟想點 而唔好盲目去追尋一啲嘢"},{"pid":"d9505f477898fbb1c49ad33d5ef61254894ab68f","tid":125694,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:23:43.000Z","msg":"retake上shitty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉 原來大學係咁無聊"},{"pid":"28a010a09c3226afe81b3642b2761bdd3871df14","tid":125694,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:24:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開始擔心畢業要出嚟乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊個唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyear1嗰陣覺得畢業仲係好遠嘅事所以冇擔心過<br />\n近排先開始發現時間過得太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最慘既係，傳說中最自由既地方，原來都只係追求現實既場所，理想既代價從來無少過</blockquote><br />\n見到d人year1已經諗定哂intern諗定哂第時做咩 讀書只為準備做野我就萬分感慨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實咁樣既，同報機器有咩分別，輸入指令: 搵錢</blockquote><br />\n識好多人成日提住個gpa<br />\n我會諗 如果大學生活就只有gpa都幾可悲</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔追求上莊，玩得癲，我開心既定義唔係呢d。<br />\n<br />\n入大學我真係想學野。但你身邊會有一班人討論gpa，然後自己都習慣左"},{"pid":"0e611562f7bc0211f41590863ab3237e920c2b3d","tid":125694,"uid":30335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:26:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n都唔知算唔算理想 可能會畀人覺得幼稚</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔想再做機器 好想改變呢個社會 唔想學生只係死讀書 想佢哋知自己究竟想點 而唔好盲目去追尋一啲嘢</blockquote><br />\n其實我都係咁諗 但完全唔知可以點做 我唔想我第時為層樓做行屍走肉 我成日覺得咁樣係好戇鳩 但同出左黎社會做野既人講就會話我唔識野 未出來做野 第時你就知 我好驚第時變成佢地咁 對生活無左熱誠只為一部機器咁"},{"pid":"65c0d1e0e745204470f0c0470c3d990093c7d2a3","tid":125694,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:26:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>開始擔心畢業要出嚟乞食<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有邊個唔驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nyear1嗰陣覺得畢業仲係好遠嘅事所以冇擔心過<br />\n近排先開始發現時間過得太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最慘既係，傳說中最自由既地方，原來都只係追求現實既場所，理想既代價從來無少過</blockquote><br />\n見到d人year1已經諗定哂intern諗定哂第時做咩 讀書只為準備做野我就萬分感慨</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實咁樣既，同報機器有咩分別，輸入指令: 搵錢</blockquote